(2, 75, '校舍簡介', 'http://', '_blank', '<div class="item-page">\r\n	<div class="page-header">\r\n		<h2>\r\n			校舍簡介\r\n		</h2>\r\n	</div>\r\n<!-- supertable debug output all exec 0.00003 gen 0.00001 tot 0.00003 end supertable debug output -->\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style="color:#DD1144;font-family:Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, ''Courier New'', monospace;font-size:10.909090995788574px;line-height:17.99715805053711px;white-space:nowrap;background-color:#EAEAEA;"><!-- supertable debug output all exec 0.00004 gen 0.00001 tot 0.00005 end supertable debug output -->\r\n<!-- supertable debug output all exec 0.00005 gen 0.00001 tot 0.00005 end supertable debug output --></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<div id="slideshow-6-52d6200050005" class="wk-slideshow wk-slideshow-tabs" data-widgetkit="slideshow" data-options="{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;tabs&quot;,&quot;autoplay&quot;:1,&quot;interval&quot;:5000,&quot;width&quot;:&quot;auto&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:&quot;auto&quot;,&quot;duration&quot;:500,&quot;index&quot;:0,&quot;order&quot;:&quot;default&quot;,&quot;navigation&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;animated&quot;:&quot;fade&quot;}">\r\n		<div class="nav-container nav-left clearfix">\r\n			<ul class="nav">\r\n				<li>\r\n					<span> 校園一景</span> \r\n				</li>\r\n				<li>\r\n					<span>禮堂</span> \r\n				</li>\r\n				<li>\r\n					<span>教堂</span> \r\n				</li>\r\n				<li>\r\n					<span>圖書館</span> \r\n				</li>\r\n				<li>\r\n					<span>教室</span> \r\n				</li>\r\n				<li>\r\n					<span>英文室</span> \r\n				</li>\r\n				<li>\r\n					<span>音樂室</span> \r\n				</li>\r\n				<li>\r\n					<span>電腦室</span> \r\n				</li>\r\n				<li>\r\n					<span>校園電視台</span> \r\n				</li>\r\n				<li>\r\n					<span>多媒體學習室</span> \r\n				</li>\r\n				<li>\r\n					<span>其他校園設施</span> \r\n				</li>\r\n				<li>\r\n					<span>小型工程項目</span> \r\n				</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class="slides-container">\r\n			<ul class="slides">\r\n				<li>\r\n					<article class="wk-content clearfix">\r\n					<div style="text-align:center;">\r\n						<img style="display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;" src="/images/SchCmps/school.JPG" alt="school" width="640" height="427" />&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img style="width:426px;height:283px;" src="/images/SchCmps/playground.JPG" alt="playground" width="420" height="280" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img style="width:424px;height:285px;" src="/images/SchCmps/running%20area.JPG" alt="running area" width="210" height="140" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img style="width:420px;height:282px;" src="/m2/images/k5.jpg" alt="" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img class="cke-resize" style="width:417px;height:280px;" src="/images/SchCmps/HALL1.JPG" alt="HALL1" width="210" height="140" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div>\r\n						<img style="display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;" src="/images/SchCmps/basketball%20playground.JPG" alt="basketball playground" width="420" height="630" /> \r\n					</div>\r\n					<div id="ckimgrsz" style="left:164.73px;top:297.398px;">\r\n						<div class="preview">\r\n							&nbsp;\r\n						</div>\r\n					</div>\r\n</article>\r\n				</li>\r\n				<li>\r\n					<article class="wk-content clearfix">\r\n					<div style="text-align:center;">\r\n						&nbsp;禮堂設有空氣調節系統，令學生在炎炎夏日<br />\r\n亦能舒適地在禮堂進行各式各樣的學習活動。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src="/m2/images/k6.jpg" alt="" width="420" height="280" /> \r\n					</div>\r\n					<div style="text-align:center;">\r\n						「即使太陽伯伯如何肆虐，<br />\r\n我們都不會再汗流浹背了！」<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src="/images/SchCmps/273.JPG" alt="273" width="420" height="280" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div style="text-align:center;">\r\n						<img src="/images/SchCmps/HALL1.JPG" alt="HALL1" width="420" /><br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<img src="/pictures/photo_59.jpg" alt="1" width="420" height="315" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n隨著資訊教育的推行，本校會在不同的場合利用資訊科技以及多媒體，故禮堂設置一幅大型電動屏幕，令在禮堂舉行的活動更生動有趣。而每一課室均設有投影器，使在課室進行教學時能以多媒體進行。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src="/pictures/photo_60.jpg" alt="1" width="420" height="315" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n禮堂設有銀幕兩組， 按不同需要使用。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src="/images/SchCmps/272.JPG" alt="272" width="420" height="280" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div style="text-align:center;">\r\n						<br />\r\n<br />\r\n					</div>\r\n</article>\r\n				</li>\r\n				<li>\r\n					<article class="wk-content clearfix">\r\n					<div>\r\n						<img style="display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;" src="/images/SchCmps/church1.JPG" alt="church1" width="420" height="280" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img style="display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;" src="/images/SchCmps/church2.JPG" alt="church2" width="420" height="280" /> \r\n					</div>\r\n</article>\r\n				</li>\r\n				<li>\r\n					<article class="wk-content clearfix">\r\n					<div style="text-align:center;">\r\n						<br />\r\n<img src="/images/SchCmps/library.JPG" alt="library" width="420" height="280" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src="/images/SchCmps/library2.JPG" alt="library2" width="420" height="280" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src="/images/SchCmps/library3.JPG" alt="library3" width="420" height="280" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src="/images/SchCmps/library4.JPG" alt="library4" width="420" height="280" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n中央圖書館是一個學習的好地方！<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src="/m2/images/k7.jpg" alt="" width="420" height="249" /> \r\n					</div>\r\n					<div style="text-align:center;">\r\n						&nbsp;<br />\r\n本校中央圖書館設置多部電腦，希望鼓勵本校學生能利用空閒時間學習資訊科技及吸收書本以外的知識。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div style="text-align:center;">\r\n						&nbsp;\r\n					</div>\r\n</article>\r\n				</li>\r\n				<li>\r\n					<article class="wk-content clearfix">\r\n					<div style="text-align:center;">\r\n						<img style="display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;" src="/images/SchCmps/classroom3.JPG" alt="classroom3" width="420" height="280" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img style="display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;" src="/images/SchCmps/classroom2.JPG" alt="classroom2" width="420" height="280" /> \r\n					</div>\r\n</article>\r\n				</li>\r\n				<li>\r\n					<article class="wk-content clearfix">\r\n					<div style="text-align:center;">\r\n						&nbsp;<img src="/images/SchCmps/english1.JPG" alt="english1" width="420" height="280" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src="/images/SchCmps/english2.JPG" alt="english2" width="420" height="283" /> \r\n					</div>\r\n					<div style="text-align:center;">\r\n						<br />\r\n<img src="/images/SchCmps/english3.JPG" alt="english3" width="420" height="280" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n英文室推行英文閱讀及寫作計劃(PLPR/W)\r\n					</div>\r\n</article>\r\n				</li>\r\n				<li>\r\n					<article class="wk-content clearfix">\r\n					<div style="text-align:center;">\r\n						&nbsp;<img src="/images/SchCmps/music%20room.JPG" alt="music room" width="420" height="280" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src="/pictures/photo_55.jpg" alt="" width="420" height="282" /> \r\n					</div>\r\n					<div style="text-align:center;">\r\n						<br />\r\n多用途室設有落地長鏡及扶手欄 供老師指導學生排練舞蹈<br />\r\n<br />\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div style="text-align:center;">\r\n						<img style="vertical-align:middle;display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;" src="/images/SchCmps/band%20room.JPG" alt="band room" width="420" height="280" /><br />\r\n爵士鼓組\r\n					</div>\r\n</article>\r\n				</li>\r\n				<li>\r\n					<article class="wk-content clearfix">\r\n					<div style="text-align:center;">\r\n						&nbsp;<img src="/images/SchCmps/computer%20room.JPG" alt="computer room" width="420" height="280" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n電腦室能容納全班同學一人一機上課，<br />\r\n讓學生更早接觸資訊科技知識。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div style="text-align:center;">\r\n						<img src="/m2/images/k9c.jpg" alt="" width="420" height="282" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n學校的新校舍設有四個特別室，底層為中央圖書館，二樓為美術室，<br />\r\n三樓為電腦室及校園電視台，四樓為多用途室。\r\n					</div>\r\n</article>\r\n				</li>\r\n				<li>\r\n					<article class="wk-content clearfix">\r\n					<p>\r\n						&nbsp;\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p align="center">\r\n						<img src="/images/SchCmps/CCTV.JPG" alt="CCTV" width="280" height="420" /> \r\n					</p>\r\n					<p align="center">\r\n						<img style="width:360px;height:270px;" src="/images/2013-09-26_11_21_26(1).jpg" alt="1" width="NaN" height="280px" /> \r\n					</p>\r\n					<p align="center">\r\n						"校園電視台"為學生帶來學習的新方向\r\n					</p>\r\n</article>\r\n				</li>\r\n				<li>\r\n					<article class="wk-content clearfix">\r\n					<p>\r\n						&nbsp;\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p align="center">\r\n						<img src="/pictures/6334.jpg" alt="1" width="360" height="270" /> \r\n					</p>\r\n					<p align="center">\r\n						新設多媒體語言實驗室,讓學生能利用最新電腦科技,<br />\r\n進行個人及小組學習活動, 使學習變得更方便,更有效率。\r\n					</p>\r\n</article>\r\n				</li>\r\n				<li>\r\n					<article class="wk-content clearfix">\r\n					<p>\r\n						&nbsp;\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p align="center">\r\n						<img src="/pictures/photo_63.jpg" alt="1" width="420" height="315" /> \r\n					</p>\r\n					<p align="center">\r\n						<img src="/pictures/photo_64.jpg" alt="1" width="420" height="315" /> \r\n					</p>\r\n					<p align="center">\r\n						地下設有座椅，讓學生及家長休息\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p align="center">\r\n						<img src="/images/SchCmps/Scholarship%20board1.JPG" alt="Scholarship board1" width="420" height="329" /> \r\n					</p>\r\n					<p align="center">\r\n						<img src="/images/SchCmps/Scholarship%20board2.JPG" alt="Scholarship board2" width="420" height="274" /> \r\n					</p>\r\n					<p align="center">\r\n						本校正門閣樓設有獎學金獲獎學生龍虎榜,展示歷年成績優異之獲獎學生。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src="/images/SchCmps/Trophy%20cabinet.JPG" alt="Trophy cabinet" width="420" height="280" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n奬盃櫃<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src="/images/SchCmps/Visual%20Arts%20Exhibition.JPG" alt="Visual Arts Exhibition" width="420" height="280" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n視藝作品陳展牆<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src="/images/SchCmps/271.JPG" alt="271" width="420" height="280" /> \r\n					</p>\r\n</article>\r\n				</li>\r\n				<li>\r\n					<article class="wk-content clearfix">\r\n					<div style="text-align:center;">\r\n						<strong><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:新細明體, serif;color:#9966cc;">&nbsp;<img src="/images/a00.jpg" alt="a00" width="240" height="97" /></span></strong> \r\n					</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n					<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" class="ke-zeroborder">\r\n						<tbody>\r\n							<tr>\r\n								<td style="width:444pt;padding:0cm;text-align:center;" valign="top" width="592">\r\n									<strong><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:新細明體, serif;">安裝節能設備</span></strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:新細明體, serif;">天台隔層塗層</span><span style="font-size:12pt;">(525</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:新細明體, serif;">㎡</span><span style="font-size:12pt;">)</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:新細明體, serif;">廚餘處理機</span><span style="font-size:12pt;">10KG</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:新細明體, serif;">容量</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:新細明體, serif;">玻璃隔熱薄膜</span><span style="font-size:12pt;">(254</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:新細明體, serif;">㎡</span><span style="font-size:12pt;">)</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n								</td>\r\n							</tr>\r\n						</tbody>\r\n					</table>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-family:新細明體, serif;">天台隔層塗層</span><span>(525</span><span style="font-family:新細明體, serif;">㎡</span><span>) - </span><span style="font-family:新細明體, serif;">禮堂頂部</span><br />\r\n<img src="/images/a02.jpg" alt="a02" width="640" height="482" /> \r\n					<div style="text-align:center;">\r\n						<br />\r\n<img src="/images/a03.jpg" alt="a03" width="640" height="480" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:10pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'', serif;"><br style="page-break-before:always;" clear="all" />\r\n</span> <span style="font-family:新細明體, serif;">玻璃隔熱薄膜</span><span>(</span><span>254</span><span style="font-family:新細明體, serif;">㎡</span><span>)</span><span>:</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src="/images/a04.jpg" alt="a04" width="640" height="480" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:新細明體, serif;letter-spacing:1pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<img src="/images/a05.jpg" alt="a05" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src="/images/a07.jpg" alt="a07" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-family:新細明體, serif;">廚餘處理機</span><span>10KG</span><span style="font-family:新細明體, serif;">容量</span> <span>– </span><span style="font-family:新細明體, serif;">禮堂出口外</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src="/images/a08.jpg" alt="a08" width="640" height="480" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n						<table border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n							<tbody>\r\n								<tr>\r\n									<td style="width:444pt;padding:0cm;" valign="top" width="592">\r\n										<strong><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:新細明體, serif;">教育活動</span></strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:新細明體, serif;">一<span>.</span>節能講座</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:新細明體, serif;letter-spacing:1pt;">二</span><span style="font-size:12pt;letter-spacing:1pt;">.</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:新細明體, serif;letter-spacing:1pt;">校內設施參觀</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:新細明體, serif;letter-spacing:1pt;">三</span><span style="font-size:12pt;letter-spacing:1pt;">.</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:新細明體, serif;letter-spacing:1pt;">環保資訊展覽</span><span style="font-size:12pt;letter-spacing:1pt;">/</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:新細明體, serif;letter-spacing:1pt;">壁佈展示</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:新細明體, serif;">透過以上各項活動，為學生介紹學校已安裝之節能設備、講解地球危機、成因、出路，當中議題包括全球暖化、節能減碳等，並講解如何在生活中實踐低碳生活。</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n									</td>\r\n								</tr>\r\n							</tbody>\r\n						</table>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong><span style="text-decoration:underline;"><span style="font-size:14pt;font-family:新細明體, serif;letter-spacing:1pt;">活動照片</span></span></strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:新細明體, serif;letter-spacing:1pt;">低年級講座</span><br />\r\n<img src="/images/a10.jpg" alt="a10" width="640" height="480" /> <strong><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:''CG Times'', serif;letter-spacing:1pt;">&nbsp; </span></strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:新細明體, serif;letter-spacing:1pt;">高年級講座</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:''CG Times'', serif;letter-spacing:1pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:新細明體, serif;letter-spacing:1pt;">節能資訊展覽</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:''CG Times'', serif;letter-spacing:1pt;">/</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:新細明體, serif;letter-spacing:1pt;">壁佈展示</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src="/images/a13.jpg" alt="a13" /><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:''CG Times'', serif;letter-spacing:1pt;">&nbsp; </span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src="/images/a14.jpg" alt="a14" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:新細明體, serif;letter-spacing:1pt;">家長曰種植展覽</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src="/images/a15.jpg" alt="a15" /><strong><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:''CG Times'', serif;letter-spacing:1pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:''CG Times'', serif;letter-spacing:1pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src="/images/a17.jpg" alt="a17" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="letter-spacing:1pt;">聖公會基愛小榮獲環境及自然保育基金撥款進行校園節能教育工程，提升能源效益和節約能源，以及減低溫室氣體排放量。</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src="/images/a11.png" alt="a11" width="160" height="160" /><img src="/images/a20.jpg" alt="a20" width="160" height="142" /> <span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> \r\n					</div>\r\n</article>\r\n				</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n</div>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2013-09-10', '2013-11-25 18:13:43', 0, 3, 1),
(3, 76, '辦學宗旨', 'http://', '_blank', '<div class="item-page">\r\n	<div class="page-header">\r\n		<h2>\r\n			辦學宗旨\r\n		</h2>\r\n	</div>\r\n<!-- supertable debug output all exec 0.00003 gen 0.00001 tot 0.00004 end supertable debug output -->\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="color:#192D35;">貫徹本校「弘德育人、有教無類、啟發潛能」的精神，培養學生正確的人生觀及關心社會，以達到德、智、體、群、美、靈六育方面的均衡發展。&nbsp;</span></span>\r\n			</p>\r\n		</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="color:#192D35;">&nbsp;本著「非以役人，乃役於人」的校訓培育學生能成為良好的公民；並鼓勵學生積極參與課外活動，發展個人的潛能。加強學校和家長的溝通，以及社會的聯繫，使學生有更多機會接觸社會，服務社群。</span></span>\r\n			</p>\r\n		</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n</div>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2013-09-10', '2013-11-25 18:13:51', 0, 4, NULL),
(4, 77, '教學政策', 'http://', '_blank', '<div class="item-page">\r\n	<div class="page-header">\r\n		<h2>\r\n			教學政策\r\n		</h2>\r\n	</div>\r\n<!-- supertable debug output all exec 0.00003 gen 0.00001 tot 0.00003 end supertable debug output -->\r\n	<p>\r\n		本校積極推動「合作學習」教學策略，以培養學生協作和溝通能力，更為學生提供不同的學習經歷，以提昇學習效益；為使每個學生都能發揮潛能，學其所得。本校除了提供正規課程外，也為學生提供多項的課餘活動。\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		本校於小一至小三落實推行小班教學，以合作學習模式進行活動，透過輪、流、講；思、討、享；互相核對、數字頭、專家組等等策略，讓學生能有更多表達個人意見的機會，加強他們學習的自信。\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<br />\r\n此外，本校為了照顧個別學生的需要，設立功課輔導支援計劃，資優課程、加強輔導計劃等等，讓學生得到較全面的照顧，發展所長。\r\n	</p>\r\n</div>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2013-09-10', '2013-11-25 18:13:54', 0, 5, 1),
