te mso 10]>\r\n<style>\r\n/* Style Definitions */\r\ntable.MsoNormalTable\r\n{mso-style-name:表格內文;\r\nmso-tstyle-rowband-size:0;\r\nmso-tstyle-colband-size:0;\r\nmso-style-noshow:yes;\r\nmso-style-priority:99;\r\nmso-style-qformat:yes;\r\nmso-style-parent:"";\r\nmso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\r\nmso-para-margin:0cm;\r\nmso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan;\r\nfont-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;\r\nfont-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0pt;}\r\n</style>\r\n<![endif]--></p>\r\n<p align="center" style="mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\nauto;text-align:center;mso-pagination:widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:\r\n13.5pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt">十一月份通訊</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: medium;"> </span></p>\r\n<p style="" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;">親愛的家長：<span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;">今年本校小一自行學位申請人數遠超收生名額，學校得以穩健發展，課程質素不斷優化，實在有賴老師及職工的努力，以及家長的支持與信任，在此表示衷心謝意。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 10</span><span style="font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;">月<span lang="EN-US">31</span>日至<span lang="EN-US">11</span>月<span lang="EN-US">3</span>日是小一至小五測驗以及小六呈分試，相信不少家長都會督促子女溫習，努力求進。正如儒家經書《禮記&middot;中庸》所說：「博學之、審問之、慎思之、明辨之、篤行之」，精要地表達學習的遞進階段。「博學」是指為學要廣泛的獵取，也意味著博大和寬容。「審問」是學的第二階段，有所不明就要追問到底。「慎思」即通過思考，分析事情箇中道理，讓所學能為己所用。「明辨」為第四階段，先有廣博的學識、精審的求知、慎密的思考，才能做到明辨學術上的真偽，明辨人事上的是非對錯。「篤行」是為學的最後階段，亦是最重要的階段，既然學有所得，就要努力實踐所學，做到「知行合一」，而具有明確的目標、堅定的意志的人，才能真正做到「篤行」。因此，家長不應只重視子女學業的成績，更須關注子女的言行及做人態度。聖經雅各書說：「快快的聽，慢慢的說，慢慢的動怒<span lang="EN-US">......</span>你們要行道，不要單單聽道<span lang="EN-US">......</span>」，當中勉勵我們要快快的聽，好好把握學習時間，除此更要在行道上熱切盡力，使道理能影響我們的內心，培育良好品格，繼續健康的成長。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;">學 校在學生品格上有明確的要求，例如學生手冊，除了讓學生記錄日常家課外，校方更希望學生透過每天記錄運動時數、閱讀時數、晚膳營養比例及填寫「我學會 了」，培養學生良好的生活習慣，為每天的生活作反思。在課程方面，各科均著重學生自學及創意的培養，而常識科、電腦專題科、聖經科亦加入實踐學習及服務學 習等元素，培養知行合一的學生。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;">十一月份逢星期一繼續舉行家校茶聚，邀請不同的專家為家長舉辦講座，分享教養子女的心得，歡迎家長出席參與。最後敬祝各位身體健康、生活愉快！</span></span></p>\r\n<p align="right" style="mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\nauto;text-align:right;text-indent:24.1pt;line-height:22.0pt;mso-pagination:\r\nwidow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;mso-font-kerning:0pt">校長 黃靜雯<span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; </span>謹啟</span><span style="mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n新細明體;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt"> </span></p>\r\n<p align="right" style="mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\nauto;text-align:right;mso-pagination:widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt">2011</span><span style="font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;mso-font-kerning:0pt">年<span lang="EN-US">11</span>月<span lang="EN-US">1</span>日</span></p>\r\n<p style="mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n新細明體;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;mso-font-kerning:0pt">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align="center" style="mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\nauto;text-align:center;mso-pagination:widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:13.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;mso-font-kerning:0pt">Monthly Newsletter(November)</span></b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n新細明體;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt"> </span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n新細明體;mso-font-kerning:0pt">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align="right" style="mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\nauto;text-align:right;line-height:18.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\r\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:新細明體;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt">1<sup>st </sup>November, 2011 </span></p>\r\n<p style="mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;">Dear Parents/Guardians, </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;"><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; T</span><span lang="EN" style="font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;">he number of applicants in the coming school year far exceeds the limit in the Discretionary Places Admission Stage. The steady progress of the school and the improvement of the curriculum have relied on the efforts of teachers and staff, and parents'' support and trust. I would like to express my sincere gratitude to thank all of you.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-size: medium;"><span lang="EN" style="font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;">Primary One to Primary Five and Primary Six students have their tests and examinations respectively from 31<sup>st</sup> October to 3<sup>rd</sup> November. &nbsp;I believe that many parents will urge their children to study hard to strive for good results. </span></span><span style="font-size: medium;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p style="" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-size: medium;"><span lang="EN" style="font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;">In a Confucian classic, <i style="mso-bidi-font-style:\r\nnormal">The Book of Rites: The Doctrine of the Mean</i>, &quot;learning extensively, inquiring acutely, deliberating deeply, discerning clearly and conducting sincerely</span><span style="font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;">&rdquo;<span lang="EN"> gives a concise expression of progressive stages of learning. &quot;Learning extensively&quot; refers to a wide range of searching for a school and also means broadness and tolerance. &quot;Inquiring acutely&quot; is the second stage of learning. If we don</span>&rsquo;<span lang="EN">t understand, then we must enquire into the root of the matter. &quot;Deliberating deeply&quot; is, through reflection, to analyze the fact so that we can put what we have learnt into practice. &quot;Discerning clearly&quot; as the fourth stage, firstly we should have completed the first three stages, and then we can discern the academic authenticity and distinguish between right and wrong. &quot;Conducting sincerely&quot; is the final stage and also the most important stage of learning, that is, to put what we have learnt into practice so that </span>&ldquo;<span lang="EN">knowledge and action are one</span>&rdquo;<span lang="EN">. &nbsp;Those who have clear objectives and a firm will can </span>&ldquo;<span lang="EN">conduct sincerely</span>&rdquo;<span lang="EN">. Therefore, parents should not only focus on their children''s academic achievements, but also be concerned about their children''s words and deeds, and their attitude towards life.</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-size: medium;"><span lang="EN" style="font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;">In the book of James in the Bible we can read, </span><span style="font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;">&ldquo;&hellip;</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;">Everyone should be quick to listen, slow to speak and slow to become angry</span><span style="font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;">&hellip;<span lang="EN-US"> Do not merely listen to the word, and so deceive yourselves</span>&rdquo;<span lang="EN-US"> (1: 19, 22).&nbsp; </span></span><span lang="EN" style="font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;">This encourages us, on one hand, to be quick to listen, take control of our study time and do what we are supposed to do. On the other hand, it encourages us to be more eager to prepare ourselves so that the truth can influence our hearts, nourish our character and enhance our health.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-size: medium;"><span lang="EN" style="font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;">The school provides clear guidance for students on conduct. For example, our student handbook is a tool to help students do self-evaluation and daily reflection. This can help them develop good living habits and reflect what they have learnt. The curriculum focuses on the cultivation of students'' self-learning skills and creativity. General Studies, I.T. project learning and Bible Studies also integrate other elements of learning by doing and service learning. Students have to apply what they have learnt in the learning process.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-size: medium;"><span lang="EN" style="font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;">Parents and Teachers Joining Hands will be held every Monday in November and we will continuously invite experts from different sectors to share parenting tips, which parents are welcome to attend. </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;">Finally, I wish you good health and happiness! <br />\r\n</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;mso-font-kerning:0pt"><br style="mso-special-character:\r\nline-break" />\r\n</span><span style="font-size: medium;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;"><br style="mso-special-character:line-break" />\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p align="right" style="mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\nauto;text-align:right;mso-pagination:widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;">Sincerely, </span></span></p>\r\n<p align="right" style="mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\nauto;text-align:right;mso-pagination:widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;">Wong Ching Man </span></span></p>\r\n<p align="right" style="mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\nauto;text-align:right;mso-pagination:widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;">Principal</span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></span></p>', '', 'http://', 1, '', 2011, '31', '', '0000-00-00', NULL);
INSERT INTO `tbl_file` (`file_id`, `file_type_id`, `file_date`, `file_exp_date`, `file_title`, `file_content`, `file_link_text`, `file_link_url`, `file_link_new_window`, `file_file_name`, `file_year`, `file_serial`, `file_add_by`, `file_add_date`, `file_photo`) VALUES
(65, 9, '2011-12-01', '0000-00-00', '聖誕佳節 常存感恩', '<p style="text-align: center; "><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; font-size: 18px; ">十二月份通訊</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: medium; ">&nbsp;<span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">親愛的家長：</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span>  </span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">近日收到不少黃大仙區的機構及教會代表讚賞本校的家校聯繫工作，為此本人對一直支持學校的家長，表示衷心的謝意。無論家校茶聚、升中講座、親子旅行及各項活動，各位家長均表現投入，令家校合作的活動得以有效推展。除此，家長教師會委員及眾家長義工亦積極協助午膳監察及活動帶隊等工作，為學校提供人力資源，使各項活動得以順利進行。</span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:新細明體;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">本校以「傳道服務」為辦學目標，在幫助學生開拓知識領域的同時，亦關注學生的心靈成長。聖誕節是紀念耶穌基督的降生，經上記著說：「道成了肉身，住在我們中間，充充滿滿的有恩典和真理。」<span lang="EN-US">(</span>約翰福音<span lang="EN-US">1:14) </span>又說：「神愛世人，甚至將祂的獨生子<span lang="EN-US">(</span>耶穌<span lang="EN-US">)</span>賜給他們，叫一切信祂的不至滅亡，反得永生。」<span lang="EN-US">(</span>約翰福音<span lang="EN-US">3:16) </span>耶穌基督為我們的罪釘死在十字架上，親身擔當了我們的罪，拯救我們脫離罪惡，使我們可享受到神對我們的疼愛與悅納。聖誕節是一個表達「愛」與「付出」的節日，願我們效法基督，攜手見證基督的大愛。十二月份學校將舉行「聖誕節崇拜暨才藝表演」，內容包括聖誕崇拜、才藝表演、合唱團獻詩、樂團表演及聖誕聯歡會，歡迎家長出席，與子女一同領受救主降臨的大喜訊息。</span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:新細明體;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">另外，為高年級學生舉辦的「古萃今承<span lang="EN-US">-</span>嶺南藝術文化」三天廣州之旅已於十一月順利完成，領隊老師包括趙曼娜主任、宗志深主任、刁美儀老師及陳仲偉老師，在此感謝老師的付出及家長對活動的支持。參與學生積極學習，透過實地考察，對嶺南藝術文化有更深的認識，活動後參與的學生亦透過匯報成果，與家長及師生分享所見所聞，實在是寶貴的學習經驗。</span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:新細明體;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">為方便家長了解學校的動向，稍後將派發本校<span lang="EN-US">2012</span>年學校年曆卡，卡上印有家校茶聚、考試及假期等資料，方便家長查閱。最後敬祝各位聖誕快樂！新年進步！</span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:新細明體;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: right; "><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 29px; ">校長 黃靜雯</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 29px; text-indent: 32px; ">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 29px; text-indent: 32px; ">謹啟</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align="right" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: right; "><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">2011</span><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">年<span lang="EN-US">12</span>月<span lang="EN-US">1</span>日</span></p>\r\n<p align="right" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: right; ">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; "><b style="text-align: center; ">