(78, 9, '2011-12-19', '0000-00-00', '善用餘暇 溫故知新', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align="center" style="text-align: center; " class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align="center" style="line-height: 150%; " class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">一月份通訊</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 150%; text-align: left; " class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">親愛的家長：<span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 29.85pt; line-height: 25pt; text-align: left; " class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">為照顧學生成長需要，本校將分階段進行陽光電話及陽光家訪活動。全校老師將於<span lang="EN-US">12</span>月及<span lang="EN-US">1</span>月份家訪小六學生，讓家長有更多機會與老師面談，討論子女升中選校及成長的需要，為孩子的成長共同努力！另外，為讓家長更了解學生的學習表現，本校於上學期及下學期舉行兩次家長觀課活動，首次活動已於<span lang="EN-US">12</span>月<span lang="EN-US">8</span>日順利舉行，觀課級別包括小一、小三及小五的中文、英文、數學科及常識科，下學期將安排其他級別進行公開課，請留意日後通告。</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 24.1pt; line-height: 25pt; text-align: left; " class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">上學期考試將至，相信家長十分關心子女的學業成績。我們知道養成持恆的溫習習慣，是提升學習成效的良方。希望家長鼓勵子女善用假期，並一同擬定溫習計劃，認真的為考測作好準備。以下是擬訂溫習計劃的小提示，供家長參考。</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="1" style="border-collapse:collapse;border:none;mso-border-alt:solid black .5pt;\r\n    mso-border-themecolor:text1;mso-yfti-tbllook:1184;mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt" class="MsoTableGrid">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="557" valign="top" style="width:418.1pt;border:solid black 1.0pt;\r\n            mso-border-themecolor:text1;mso-border-alt:solid black .5pt;mso-border-themecolor:\r\n            text1;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt">\r\n            <p style="mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\n            line-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-pagination:widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">擬定溫習計劃小提示</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            <p style="mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\n            line-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-pagination:widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">( 1 ) </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">各科平衡發展</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            <ul>\r\n                <li><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Wingdings; "><span style="font: normal normal normal 7pt/normal ''Times New Roman''; "> </span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">每科的溫習時間應該平均，但可因應情況放多些時間溫習成績較弱科目</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></li>\r\n            </ul>\r\n            <p style="mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\n            line-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-pagination:widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">( 2 ) </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">作息有序</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            <ul>\r\n                <li><span style="font-size: medium; "><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">須考慮平衡學習、休息、娛樂等安排，如溫習時段為一小時，期間可加入約五至十分鐘的小休，放鬆心情，讓專注力更持久</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></li>\r\n            </ul>\r\n            <p style="mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\n            line-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-pagination:widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">( 3 ) </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">注意可行性</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            <ul>\r\n                <li><span style="font-size: medium; "><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">要考慮自己的能力，計劃中可預留一些空間&mdash;&mdash;「備用時間」，調節溫習進度</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></li>\r\n            </ul>\r\n            <p style="mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\n            line-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-pagination:widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">( 4 ) </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">適時檢討及自我獎勵</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            <ul>\r\n                <li><span style="font-size: medium; "><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">如能按照計劃執行，可在「備用時間」加入一些娛樂以作鼓勵。如未能達標，亦可善用此時段加以溫習</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></li>\r\n            </ul>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 25pt; text-align: left; " class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">聖誕將至，願我們一同記念主耶穌基督的降生，享受歡樂時光。在此敬祝各位</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left; " class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">聖誕快樂！新年進步！</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p align="right" style="mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\nauto;text-align:right;mso-pagination:widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">校長 黃靜雯</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">謹啟</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p align="right" style="mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\nauto;text-align:right;mso-pagination:widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">2011</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">年<span lang="EN-US">12</span>月<span lang="EN-US">19</span>日</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p align="center" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">Monthly Newsletter(January)</span></b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p align="right" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:right;line-height:18.0pt;\r\nmso-line-height-rule:exactly">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align="right" style="line-height: 18pt; " class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:新細明體;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt">19<sup>th </sup>December, 2011&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align="center" class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left; " class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">Dear Parents,</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 24pt; text-align: left; " class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">To cater for the developmental needs of students, the school will have the Sunshine phone calls and home visits. </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">Teachers will conduct home visits in December and January for primary six students.&nbsp; The home visits will give you more opportunities to communicate directly with teachers to </span><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">discuss</span><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); "> </span><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">their children</span><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">''s </span><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">choice</span><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); "> of school </span><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">and growth</span><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); "> </span><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">needs</span><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">. In addition, in order to allow you to better understand the performance of students, lesson observations are arranged twice a year. </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">Lesson observations were successfully held on 8 December for P.1, P.3 and P.5 classes in Chinese, English, Mathematics and General Studies lessons. In the next term, we will arrange lesson observations for other levels. Please note the information in the coming term.</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align: top; text-align: left; " class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; The second term is coming and I believe that you are very concerned about your child''s academic performance. We all know that the habit of doing revision regularly is one way to enhance learning. I hope that you will encourage your child to make good use of the holiday, make a study plan together and carefully prepare for tests and examinations. The following tips are for your reference to develop a study plan with your child.</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="1" style="border-collapse:collapse;border:none;mso-border-alt:solid black .5pt;\r\n    mso-border-themecolor:text1;mso-yfti-tbllook:1184;mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt" class="MsoTableGrid">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="557" valign="top" style="width:418.1pt;border:solid black 1.0pt;\r\n            mso-border-themecolor:text1;mso-border-alt:solid black .5pt;mso-border-themecolor:\r\n            text1;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt">\r\n            <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><b><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">Tips for Developing a Study Plan</span></b></span><b><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n            <ol>\r\n                <li><span style="font-size: medium;"><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體,serif;">balanced revision of subjects<br />\r\n                </span></span><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">             The study time for each subject should be balanced but children may spend more   time on subjects they have more difficulty in</span></span><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><o:p></o:p></span>.<br />\r\n                &nbsp;</li>\r\n                <li><span style="font-size: medium;"><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體,serif;">balance between rest and learning<br />\r\n                Consider the balance among study, rest, recreation and other arrangements. A   5-10 minute break within aone-hour study period can let your children relax   and maintain a longer concentration span.</span></span><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><o:p></o:p></span><br />\r\n                &nbsp;</li>\r\n                <li><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><span style="font: normal normal normal 7pt/normal ''Times New Roman''; "> </span></span><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">awareness of feasibility<br />\r\n                Consider individual ability. You may set some space or &quot;spare time&quot;   to regulate the progress of studying.</span></span><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><o:p></o:p></span><br />\r\n                &nbsp;</li>\r\n                <li><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">review and self-reward<br />\r\n                According to the plan implemented, spare time and entertainment can be added as   encouragement. If your child cannot meet the target, they may need to spend   the time for encouragement in revising.</span></span><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n            </ol>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-align: left; " class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">Christmas </span><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">is coming. I wish you all a Merry Christmas and a Happy</span><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); "> </span><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">New Year!</span></span><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p align="right" style="mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\nauto;text-align:right;mso-pagination:widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">Sincerely,</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p align="right" style="mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\nauto;text-align:right;mso-pagination:widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">Wong Ching Man</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p align="right" style="mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\nauto;text-align:right;mso-pagination:widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">Principal</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><o:p></o:p></span><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><o:p></o:p></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:新細明體;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '', 'http://', 1, '', 2011, '31', '', '0000-00-00', NULL),
(79, 9, '2012-01-16', '0000-00-00', '新年蒙福 關愛洋溢', '<p style="text-align: center; "><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: center; ">二月份通訊</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><v:shapetype id="_x0000_t4" coordsize="21600,21600" o:spt="4" path="m10800,l,10800,10800,21600,21600,10800xe">  <v:stroke joinstyle="miter"></v:stroke>  <v:path gradientshapeok="t" o:connecttype="rect" textboxrect="5400,5400,16200,16200"></v:path> </v:shapetype><v:shape id="_x0000_s1026" type="#_x0000_t4" style="position:absolute;\r\nmargin-left:220.05pt;margin-top:-77.05pt;width:71.4pt;height:73.15pt;\r\nz-index:251660288">  <v:textbox>\r\n<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <div>\r\n            <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:30.0pt;\r\n            mso-line-height-rule:exactly"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal"><span style="font-size:30.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\n            major-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\n            major-fareast"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</v:textbox> </v:shape><span style="font-size: medium; "><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">親愛的家長：<span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-fareast;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-fareast"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">農曆新年將至，中國人大都喜歡在家掛上「福」字的揮春，象徵對新一年的祝願。聖經中亦多次提及「福」，人要蒙福，就須要走蒙福的路，在農曆新年歡樂的節日，讓我們一同從聖經認識蒙福的途徑，並教導孩童，使我們及下一代得福。</span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-fareast"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-fareast"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<table class="MsoNormalTable" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="border-collapse:collapse;border:none;mso-border-alt:double windowtext 1.5pt;\r\n    mso-yfti-tbllook:1184;mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;mso-border-insideh:\r\n    1.5pt double windowtext;mso-border-insidev:1.5pt double windowtext">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="684" valign="top" style="width:513.0pt;border:double windowtext 1.5pt;\r\n            padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt">\r\n            <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; "><span style="font-size: medium; "><b><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">《蒙福的途徑》</span></b></span><b><span style="font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-fareast;\r\n            mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-fareast"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n            <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:\r\n            l0 level1 lfo1"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">1.<span style="font: normal normal normal 7pt/normal ''Times New Roman''; ">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">敬畏神、認識真道</span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-fareast;\r\n            mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-fareast"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">詩篇<span lang="EN-US">128</span>篇<span lang="EN-US">1</span>節：「凡敬畏耶和華、遵行他道的人，便&#29234;有福。」</span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\n            major-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-fareast"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">雅各書<span lang="EN-US">1</span>章<span lang="EN-US">22</span>節：「只是你們要行道，不要單單聽道。」中國傳統文化的代表人物孔子亦說過：「坐而論道，不如起而行之。」多行善事，遵守聖經的教訓，必然得福。   </span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\n            major-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-fareast"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\n            mso-ascii-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;\r\n            mso-hansi-theme-font:major-fareast"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:\r\n            l0 level1 lfo1"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">2.<span style="font: normal normal normal 7pt/normal ''Times New Roman''; ">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">喜愛智慧、追求知識</span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-fareast;\r\n            mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-fareast"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">詩篇<span lang="EN-US">1</span>篇<span lang="EN-US">1</span>至<span lang="EN-US">2</span>節：「不從惡人的計謀，不站罪人的道路，不坐褻慢人的座位，惟喜愛耶和華的律法，晝夜思想，這人便為有福。」箴言<span lang="EN-US">3</span>章<span lang="EN-US">13</span>至<span lang="EN-US">15</span>節：「得智慧、得聰明，這人便&#29234;有福。因&#29234;得智慧勝過得銀子，其利益強如精金，比珍珠寶貴，你一切所喜愛的，都不足與比較。」智慧能伴隨我們一生，我們常說：「知識是力量」，因為智慧和知識讓我們有能力面對人生的挑戰，在當中到平安。   </span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\n            major-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-fareast"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\n            mso-ascii-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;\r\n            mso-hansi-theme-font:major-fareast"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">3. </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">榮神益人、顧己及人</span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\n            mso-ascii-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;\r\n            mso-hansi-theme-font:major-fareast"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">創世記<span lang="EN-US">12</span>章<span lang="EN-US">2</span>節提及神對亞伯拉罕說：「我必賜福給你，叫你的名&#29234;大，你也要叫別人得福。」哥林多前書<span lang="EN-US">10</span>章<span lang="EN-US">23</span>至<span lang="EN-US">24</span>節：「凡事都可行，但不都有益處；凡事都可行，但不都造就人。無論何人，不要求自己的益處，乃要求別人的益處。」每個人的行為都會影響身邊的人，一個行為正直，愛神愛人的人，必能為自己和身邊的人帶來祝福。</span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\n            major-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-fareast"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\n            mso-ascii-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;\r\n            mso-hansi-theme-font:major-fareast"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-fareast"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">願新一年我們繼續互相分享，彼此勸勉，為我們的家人及朋友代禱，求神的祝福，讓關愛洋溢基慈小學。另外，本校將於</span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-fareast"><st1:chsdate year="2012" month="2" day="11" islunardate="False" isrocdate="False" w:st="on"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN-US">2</span>月<span lang="EN-US">11</span>日</span></st1:chsdate><span style="font-size: medium; ">舉行「家長日」，讓家長與班主任面談，了解子女在校的情況，交流教養心得，誠邀家長出席。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">最後敬祝各位新春快樂！主恩常偕！</span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: right; "><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 29px; ">校長 黃靜雯</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 29px; text-indent: 32px; ">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 29px; text-indent: 32px; ">謹啟</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align="right" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: right; "><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">2012</span><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">年<span lang="EN-US">1</span>月<span lang="EN-US">16</span>日</span></p>\r\n<p align="right" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: right; ">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; "><b style="text-align: center; "><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">Monthly Newsletter(February)</span></b>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="1" style="word-break: break-all; text-align: right; "><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; ">16<sup>th </sup>January</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; ">, 20</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; ">12<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">Dear Parents,</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-fareast"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:24.0pt"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">At Lunar New Year, Chinese people like putting up red paper with the Chinese word &ldquo;fortune&rdquo; at home, which is a symbol of blessing. This word is found throughout the Bible. We need to follow the way to be blessed if we want to be blessed. Let us be blessed and understand the way from the Bible and lead our children and our generation to the way of being blessed.</span></span><span lang="EN" style="font-family:\r\n&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-ansi-language:EN"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<table class="MsoTableGrid" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="border-collapse:collapse;border:none;mso-border-alt:solid black .5pt;\r\n    mso-border-themecolor:text1;mso-yfti-tbllook:1184;mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="557" valign="top" style="width:418.1pt;border:solid black 1.0pt;\r\n            mso-border-themecolor:text1;mso-border-alt:solid black .5pt;mso-border-themecolor:\r\n            text1;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt">\r\n            <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">&quot;Blessed Way&quot;</span></span><span lang="EN" style="font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-fareast;\r\n            mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-fareast;\r\n            mso-ansi-language:EN"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">1. Fear God,   Understand the Truth</span></span></p>\r\n            <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">&ldquo;</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">Blessed   are all who fear the Lord, who walk in obedience to him&rdquo; (</span><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">Psalm 128:1)</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">.</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:\r\n            &quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\n            major-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-fareast"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">&ldquo;Do not merely listen to the word, and so   deceive yourselves. Do what it says&rdquo; (</span><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">James   1:22)</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">.</span></span></p>\r\n            <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">In the Chinese   culture, there is also the saying, <b>&ldquo;</b></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">Sitting   to discuss the right thing to do is not as beneficial as getting up and doing   it</span><b><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">&rdquo;</span></b><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "> (Confucius).&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n            <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">If we do follow the   lessons in the Bible, we will be blessed.</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-fareast;\r\n            mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-fareast"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">2. Through the   Pursuit of Knowledge Comes Wisdom</span></span><span lang="EN" style="font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\n            mso-ascii-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;\r\n            mso-hansi-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-ansi-language:EN"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">&ldquo;Blessed is the one who does not walk in   step with the wicked or stand in the way that sinners take or sit in the   company of mockers, but whose delight is in the law of the Lord, and who   meditates on his law day and night&rdquo; (Psalm 1:1-2).</span></span><span lang="EN" style="font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-fareast;\r\n            mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-fareast;\r\n            mso-ansi-language:EN"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">&ldquo;Blessed are those who find wisdom, those   who gain understanding, for she is more profitable than silver and yields   better returns than gold. She is more precious than rubies; nothing you   desire can compare with her&rdquo; (</span><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">Proverbs 3:13-15)</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">.&nbsp; </span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-fareast;\r\n            mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-fareast"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">The wisdom you gain is life-long.&nbsp; We often say, &ldquo;Knowledge is power&rdquo; because   with wisdom and knowledge, we have the ability to face life&rsquo;s challenges with   peace. </span></span><span lang="EN" style="font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\n            major-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-fareast;\r\n            mso-ansi-language:EN"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">3. Be a Blessing and   Considerate To Others</span></span><span lang="EN" style="font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\n            mso-ascii-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;\r\n            mso-hansi-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-ansi-language:EN"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">In Genesis, God said   to Abraham, &ldquo;</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">I will make you into a great nation, and   I will bless you; I will make your name great, and you will be a blessing&rdquo;   (Genesis 12:2).</span></span><span lang="EN" style="font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\n            mso-ascii-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;\r\n            mso-hansi-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-ansi-language:EN"><o:p></o:p></span><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">&ldquo;I have the right to do anything, &lsquo;you   say&mdash;but not everything is beneficial. &lsquo;I have the right to do anything&rsquo;&mdash;but   not everything is constructive. &nbsp;No one   should seek their own good, but the good of others&rdquo; (1 Corinthians 10:23-24).</span></span><span lang="EN" style="font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-fareast;\r\n            mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-fareast;\r\n            mso-ansi-language:EN"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">A person&rsquo;s behaviour   will affect everyone around them. People who love God and others can bring   blessings to themselves and the people around them.</span></span><span lang="EN" style="font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\n            mso-ascii-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;\r\n            mso-hansi-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-ansi-language:EN"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></span><span lang="EN" style="font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\n            mso-ascii-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;\r\n            mso-hansi-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-ansi-language:EN"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></span><span lang="EN" style="font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-fareast;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN"><o:p></o:p></span><font face="新細明體, serif" size="3"><br />\r\n</font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">Let&rsquo;s continue to share, encourage one another and pray for our family and friends in the New Year. Let God''s blessing fill Kei Tsz Primary School with love. In addition, Parents Day will be held on 11<sup>th</sup> February. It&rsquo;s an opportunity to let parents and teachers understand children&rsquo;s performance in school and exchange parenting tips. Parents are most welcome to attend.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; "><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Finally, I wish you a Happy New Year! </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">May the love of God be with you always</span><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">!</span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: right; ">&nbsp;<span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">Sincerely,</span></span></p>\r\n<p align="right" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: right; "><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">Wong Ching Man</span></span></p>\r\n<p align="right" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: right; "><span style="font-size: medium; "><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif; ">Principal</span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-fareast;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-fareast"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-fareast"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>', '', 'http://', 1, '', 2011, '31', '', '0000-00-00', NULL);
