(9, 1, '中文科', '', NULL, '<div class="item-page">\r\n	<div class="page-header">\r\n		<h2>\r\n			中文\r\n		</h2>\r\n	</div>\r\n<!-- supertable debug output all exec 0.00003 gen 0.00001 tot 0.00004 end supertable debug output -->\r\n	<p>\r\n		(一) 課程簡介\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		本校中文科課程一直按學生需要及配合教育局課程的要求，不斷作出改革，如閱讀策略、提問技巧及合作學習策略，務求讓學生樂於學習、有效學習。\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		中文科着重以學生為主的教學模式，透過正規課程及多元化的活動，如說話活動、小組閱讀分享、午間廣播、網上練習、投稿園地、校際朗誦比賽、標語比賽、徵文比賽、書法比賽等，誘發學生對學習中國語文的興趣。本校致力提升學生兩文三語的能力，小一至小二、小三至小六精英班均以普通話教授中文，並鼓勵師生於課餘時以普通話交談，為學生營造語境，增加練習機會。\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&nbsp;<br />\r\n(二) 課程宗旨\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="PlainText">\r\n		主要教學目標\r\n	</p>\r\n	<ol>\r\n		<li>\r\n			指導學生掌握閱讀策略，培養學生對語文的閱讀和理解能力。\r\n		</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			指導學生閱讀課外讀物，養成閱讀的興趣和習慣。\r\n		</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			指導學生運用語文來表達思想，使具有寫作的基本能力。\r\n		</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			指導學生正確的寫字姿勢和執筆，運筆的方法，使能達到書寫正確，迅速<span style="font-size:12px;">和整潔的目標。</span>\r\n		</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			<span style="font-size:12px;">培養學生聆聽和說話的能力和應有的態度。</span>\r\n		</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			<span style="font-size:12px;">指導學生閱讀文學作品，欣賞文學之美。</span>\r\n		</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			<span style="font-size:12px;">認識中華文化，培養對國家、民族的感情。</span>\r\n		</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			<span style="font-size:12px;">透過語文學習，陶冶學生的性情，培養良好的品德及加強對社群的責任感。</span>\r\n		</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			<span style="font-size:12px;">培養學生具批判性、創作性思考能力和解決問題的能力。</span>\r\n		</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			<span style="font-size:12px;">指導學生運用詞典、字典的方法和養成運用工具書的習慣，培養自學能力。</span>\r\n		</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			<span style="font-size:12px;">透過適切的教學語言(粵語或普通話)，發展學生的思維能力，培養學生對</span><span style="font-size:12px;">語文學習的興趣。</span>\r\n		</li>\r\n	</ol>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		(三) 學習範疇\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		以九個學習範疇(閱讀、寫作、聆聽、說話、文學、中華文化、品德情意、思維、語文自學)進行教學，當中以讀寫聽說為主導，帶動其他範疇學習，建構知識，培養共通能力、價值觀和態度。\r\n	</p>\r\n	<table style="width:580px;height:152px;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n		<tbody>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td valign="top" width="103">\r\n					<p align="center">\r\n						範疇\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td valign="top" width="543">\r\n					<p align="center">\r\n						教學目標\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td valign="top" width="103">\r\n					<p align="center">\r\n						閱讀\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td valign="top" width="543">\r\n					<p>\r\n						培養理解、分析、評價、鑑賞的能力/掌握閱讀策略/樂於閱讀、勤於閱讀、認真閱讀\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td valign="top" width="103">\r\n					<p align="center">\r\n						寫作\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td valign="top" width="543">\r\n					<p>\r\n						培養組織結構、表達、創作的能力/掌握寫作策略/樂於寫作、勤於寫作、認真寫作\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td valign="top" width="103">\r\n					<p align="center">\r\n						聆聽\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td valign="top" width="543">\r\n					<p>\r\n						培養理解、評價的能力/掌握聆聽策略/樂於聆聽、認真聆聽\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td valign="top" width="103">\r\n					<p align="center">\r\n						說話\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td valign="top" width="543">\r\n					<p>\r\n						培養組織結構、口語表達的能力/掌握說話策略/樂於表達、勇於表達、適當應對\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td valign="top" width="103">\r\n					<p align="center">\r\n						文學\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td valign="top" width="543">\r\n					<p>\r\n						透過文學的學習，感受語文的美感，提高學習語文的興趣和語文能力\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td valign="top" width="103">\r\n					<p align="center">\r\n						中華文化\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td valign="top" width="543">\r\n					<p>\r\n						學習蘊含中華文化的材料，增進對中華文化的認識，培養對國家、民族的感情\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td valign="top" width="103">\r\n					<p align="center">\r\n						品德情意\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td valign="top" width="543">\r\n					<p>\r\n						培養道德情操與積極的人生態度，加強對社會的責任感\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td valign="top" width="103">\r\n					<p align="center">\r\n						思維\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td valign="top" width="543">\r\n					<p>\r\n						培養批判性、創造性思考能力和解決問題的能力\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td valign="top" width="103">\r\n					<p align="center">\r\n						語文自學\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td valign="top" width="543">\r\n					<p>\r\n						培養獲取知識、建構知識、運用知識及自我監控的能力，從而提高語文自學的興趣\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		(四) 近期活動\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		「午間逍遙音樂之旅」\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		與音樂科合辦「午間逍遙音樂之旅」，以獎賞形式鼓勵學生，每月透過填寫音樂回應表，利用文字表達對音樂類型的喜好及感受，鼓勵學生多思考、積極表達意見，以培養學生批判思考能力。\r\n	</p>\r\n</div>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0000-00-00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(16, 1, '英文 (English Language)	', '', NULL, '<div class="page-header">\r\n	<h2>\r\n		英文 (English Language)\r\n	</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- supertable debug output all exec 0.00003 gen 0.00001 tot 0.00003 end supertable debug output -->\r\n<p style="text-align:left;" align="center">\r\n	1. Curriculum Introduction\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	A language-rich learning environment is created to develop students’ interest and build up their confidence in learning English. More importantly, students will have the opportunity to communicate in English with native speakers such as students from an international school and graduates from Oxford University.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	2. Aims\r\n</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		To provide opportunities for students to acquire, develop, and become proficient in the English language through listening, speaking, reading and writing.\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		To provide every student a second language with further opportunities for extending their knowledge and experience of the cultures of other people as well as opportunities for personal and intellectual development, further studies, pleasure and work in the English medium.\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n	3. Special features of our English Curriculum\r\n</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Every student from P1 to P6 must learn the “Read-Aloud-and-Write Phonetic Method” to develop their basic skills in pronunciation and reading aloud plus spelling.\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		We provide intensive grammar learning in the school-based English curriculum.\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		We have a school-based reading curriculum for P1-P3 students in collaboration with the NET (Native English Teacher) and a classroom assistant.\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		We have a school-based special reading and writing curriculum funded by EEGS(English Enhancement Grant Scheme for Primary Schools) for P4-P6 students.\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		We have Fun Fun English Groups (with native English speaking senior students) for P4-6 students on Saturday mornings. Students come from Sha Tin College, an international school.\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		We have one additional NET for P4-P6 students to enhance their reading and speaking skills.\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n	4. Recent English activity\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Ocean Park Visit\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0000-00-00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 2);
